- Y: annulus 4<r≤6, area = π(6^2−4^2) = 36π−16π = 20π.
- Z: outer annulus 6<r≤7, area = π(7^2−6^2) = 49π−36π = 13π.
- Greatest = 20π, smallest = 13π, difference = 7π.

