- e^{iπ/4} = (1+i)/√2, so w − c = (1/√2)(1+i)·√2(1−3i) = (1+i)(1−3i) = 4 − 2i.
- w = c + (4 − 2i) = (2 − 3i) + (4 − 2i) = 6 − 5i.

